""SELECT [h].[Id], [h].[Address], [h].[City], [h].[Description], [h].[Hotel Rating], [h].[Name], [h].[Pincode], [h].[State], [h].[Status]
FROM [Hotel] AS [h]
WHERE CAST([h].[Hotel Rating] AS int) IN (1, 2, 3, 4, 5) AND (((
    SELECT MIN([h0].[Rate])
    FROM [HotelRooms] AS [h0]
    WHERE [h].[Id] = [h0].[Hotel Id]) >= @__p_1) AND ((
    SELECT MIN([h1].[Rate])
    FROM [HotelRooms] AS [h1]
    WHERE [h].[Id] = [h1].[Hotel Id]) <= @__p_2))
ORDER BY [h].[Hotel Rating] DESC
OFFSET @__p_3 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_4 ROWS ONLY"

WHERE (((((@__p_0 = N'') OR (LEFT([h].[Name], LEN(@__p_0)) = @__p_0)) OR ((@__p_1 = N'') OR (LEFT([h].[City], LEN(@__p_1)) = @__p_1))) OR ([h].[Pincode] = @__p_2)) AND CAST([h].[Hotel Rating] AS int) IN (1, 2, 3, 4, 5)) AND (((
    SELECT MIN([h0].[Rate])
    FROM [HotelRooms] AS [h0]
    WHERE [h].[Id] = [h0].[Hotel Id]) >= @__p_4) AND ((
    SELECT MIN([h1].[Rate])
    FROM [HotelRooms] AS [h1]
    WHERE [h].[Id] = [h1].[Hotel Id]) <= @__p_5))
ORDER BY (SELECT 1)
OFFSET @__p_6 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_7 ROWS ONLY"
